quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  22,6,Zimenezo ndi chifukwa chakuti Mulungu ndiye choonadi ndipo Iye amapereka moyo ku zinthu zakufa ndipo ali ndi mphamvu pa chinthu china chilichonse
  22,7,Ndithudi ola lili nkudza mosakayika pamene Mulungu adzawadzutsa onse amene ali m’manda
  22,8,Ndipo pakati pa anthu pali wina amene amatsutsa za Mulungu pamene sakudziwa chilichonse ndiponso chilangizo kapena Buku la chivumbulutso
  22,9,"Munthu wotere amathyola khosi monyadira ndi kusocheza ena ku njira ya Mulungu. Kwa otere kuli mnyozo m’moyo uno ndipo patsiku louka kwa akufa, tidzamulawitsa chilango cha moto woyaka"
  22,10,"“Izi ndi chifukwa cha zomwe manja anu adatsogoza ndipo, ndithudi, Mulungu sapondereza akapolo ake"
  22,11,Ndipo pakati pa anthu pamakhala munthu amene amampembedza Mulungu mokayikira. Zikapezeka zabwino amakhala wokhutitsidwa ndi izo koma ngati mavuto amugwera amatembenuka motero; iye amataya zabwino za m’moyo uno ndi za m’moyo umene uli nkudza. Kumeneko ndiko kulephera koonekeratu
  22,12,"Iwo amapempha mowonjezera pa Mulungu, zimene sizingathe kumuononga kapena kumuthandiza. Kumeneko ndiko kusochera kwenikweni"
  22,13,"Amapempha kwa iye amene mavuto ake ali pafupi kuposa chithandizo chake. Iye, ndithudi, ndi mtsogoleri woipa ndiponso bwenzi loipa"
  22,14,Ndithudi Mulungu adzawalowetsa onse amene amakhulupilira ndipo amachita ntchito zabwino m’minda yothiriridwa ndi mitsinje ndi madzi oyenda. Ndithudi Mulungu amachita zimene afuna
  22,15,"Ngati wina aganiza kuti Mulungu sadzathandiza Mtumwi wake m’dziko lino ndi m’dziko limene lili nkudza, mulekeni amange chingwe ku phaso la nyumba yake ndi kudzimangirira yekha. Ndipo mulekeni kuti awone yekha ngati cholinga chake chingachotse vuto lomwe limamukwiyitsa iye"